48,"file_path":"/gIfaKuKgqVCJ2cn3EaMs76cMtEy.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-26T03:36:54.02+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Fast & Furious 7","runtime":137,"tagline":"La vengeance est proche.","homepage":"","overview":"Laiss├Е ├а moiti├Е mort par Dominic Toretto et son clan de voleur de voitures as du volant, le criminel Owen Shaw g├«t sur un lit d'h├┤pital ├а Londres. D├Еtermin├Е ├а le venger, son fr├еre Deckard Shaw commet des attaques vicieuses contre les membres de la famille de Toretto, notamment contre sa s┼Њur, son beau-fr├еre et leur petit gar├Дon. Une aide inesp├Еr├Еe leur parvient en la personne de Frank Petty, agent des services secrets am├Еricains aux ressources impressionnantes. Il promet assistance ├а Dominic, en ├Еchange de quoi ce dernier devra lib├Еrer une talentueuse informaticienne, nomm├Еe Ramsey, qui a mis au point un logiciel de surveillance ultraperfectionn├Е baptis├Е ┬Ф God's Eye ┬╗. La jeune femme est en effet retenue prisonni├еre par Jakande, un dangereux terroriste, au milieu des inaccessibles montagnes de l'Azerba├»djan. Le clan de Dominic se reforme donc pour cette dangereuse mission."},"name":"Fran├Дais","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Fast & Furious 7","runtime":137,"tagline":"Zeit f├╝r Vergeltung","homepage":"http://www.fast7-film.de/","overview":"Nachdem Dominic Toretto und sein Team den B├Хsewicht Owen Shaw ausgeschaltet haben, sinnt dessen Bruder Deckard nach blutiger Rache. Doch der ist nicht ihr einziges Problem. Die Bleifu├Ъ-Freunde sollen n├цmlich gleichzeitig - im Auftrag eines mysteri├Хsen Agenten namens Mr. Nobody - heimt├╝ckischen Terroristen ein \"Das Auge Gottes\" genanntes GPS-Programm abjagen und die Programmiererin Ramsey aus deren H├цnden befreien. Also klemmt sich die Crew noch einmal hinters Steuer und trotzt dabei mehrfach der Schwerkraft."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Fast & Furious 7","runtime":137,"tagline":"La vendetta colpisce in casa","homepage":"http://www.fastandfurious.com/","overview":"Un anno dopo essere ritornati negli Stati Uniti, Dom Toretto (Vin Diesel) e la sua banda di amici piloti si ritrovano costretti ad affrontare il piano di vendetta di Deckard Shaw (Jason Statham), determinato a far giustizia a modo proprio per la morte del fratello avvenuto anni prima. Ad aiutare Toretto e i suoi uomini sar├а un enigmatico agente governativo (Kurt Russell), che propone loro in cambio di aiuto di testare sulle loro auto un dispositivo federale segreto."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":139,"tagline":"Vengeance hits home.","homepage":"https://www.uphe.com/movies/furious-7","overview":"Deckard Shaw seeks revenge against Dominic Toretto and his family for his comatose brother."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"жђЪт║дСИјТ┐ђТЃЁ7","runtime":137,"tagline":"тјЪуЈГС║║жЕг С╗ЦуЅЎУ┐ўуЅЎ","homepage":"","overview":"у╗ЈтјєС║єу┤Дт╝атѕ║Т┐ђуџёС╝дТЋдтцДТѕў№╝їтцџу▒│т░╝тЁІ┬иТЅўУј▒тцџ№╝ѕУїЃ┬иУ┐фтАът░ћ Vin Diesel жЦ░№╝ЅтњїС╗ќуџёС╝ЎС╝┤С╗гжЄЇТќ░тЏътйњт╣│жЮЎуџёућЪТ┤╗№╝їСйєТў»Т▒ЪТ╣ќуџёТЂЕТЂЕТђеТђетЇ┤тє│СИЇтЁЂУ«ИС╗ќС╗гУй╗ТўЊТійУ║ФУђїтј╗сђѓТБўТЅІуџёТГ╗т»╣тц┤ТгДТќЄ┬иУѓќуўФтюетї╗жЎб№╝їСИЇтЙЌтіет╝╣№╝їС╗ќуџётЊЦтЊЦТѕ┤тЁІ┬иУѓќ№╝ѕТЮ░ТБ«┬иТќ»тЮдТБ« Jason Stantham жЦ░№╝ЅтѕЎтЈЉУфЊУдЂСИ║т╝Ът╝ЪтцЇС╗ЄсђѓТѕ┤тЁІТЏЙТў»УІ▒тЏйуЅ╣уДЇжЃежўЪуџёујІуЅїТЮђТЅІ№╝їСИЇС╗ЁУ║ФТђђу╗ЮТіђ№╝їУђїСИћт┐ЃуІаТЅІУЙБсђѓС╗ќт╣▓ТјЅС║єУ┐ютюеСИюС║гуџёжЪЕ№╝їУ┐ўтЄаС╣јТііТјбжЋ┐тЇбтЁІ┬ижюЇтИЃТќ»№╝ѕжЂЊТЂЕ┬ит╝║ТБ« Dwayne Johnson жЦ░№╝ЅжђЂтѕ░тЈдСИђСИфСИќуЋї№╝їућџУЄ│тцџу▒│т░╝тЁІжѓБСИќтцќТАЃТ║љУѕгуџёт«ХС╣ЪУбФт»╣Тќ╣уѓИТ»ЂсђѓтцЇС╗ЄуџётѕЕтѕЃти▓у╗ЈТъХтюеУёќтГљСИі№╝їтцџу▒│т░╝тЁІтєЇС╣ЪТ▓АТюЅжђЅТІЕ№╝їС╗ќТЅЙтѕ░жЋ┐С╣ЁС╗ЦТЮЦТюђСИ║С┐АУхќуџётЏбжўЪ№╝їСИјТЮЦті┐Т▒╣Т▒╣уџёТѕ┤тЁІт▒Ћт╝ђућЪТГ╗т»╣тє│РђдРђд"},"name":"ТЎ«жђџУ»Ю","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Rychle a zb─Џsile 7","runtime":137,"tagline":"Pomsta se vrac├Г dom┼».","homepage":"","overview":"I auta m┼»┼Йou l├Еtat. Alespo┼ѕ pro nesmrtelnou s├Еrii Rychle a zb─Џsile to plat├Г. Jej├Г hrdinov├Е u┼Й stihli pro┼Й├Гt a p┼Ўe┼Й├Гt neuv─Џ┼Ўiteln├Е v─Џci, te─Ј v┼Аak naraz├Г na nep┼Ў├Гtele, vedle n─Џho┼Й v┼Аichni jejich dosavadn├Г soupe┼Ўi p┼Ўipom├Гnaj├Г bandu d─Џt├Г z mate┼Ўsk├Е ┼Аkolky. Statham hraje Deckarda Shawa, ┼Йiv├й stroj na zab├Гjen├Г, kter├й vycvi─Їila elitn├Г vojensk├А jednotka. Pokud v├Аm p┼Ў├Гjmen├Г t├Еhle postavy n─Џco p┼Ўipom├Гn├А, pak se nepletete. Shaw┼»v mlad┼А├Г bratr Owen obt─Џ┼Йoval na┼Аe hrdiny v ┼Аest├Еm d├Гle tak intenzivn─Џ, a┼Й ho p┼Ўipravili o ┼Йivot. A rozru┼Аen├й Shaw star┼А├Г se rozhodne, ┼Йe na opl├Аtku p┼Ўiprav├Г o ┼Йivot je a v┼Аechny jejich bl├Гzk├Е. Bez ohledu na to, jak rychl├Г ─Їi zb─Џsil├Г budou."},"name":"─їesk├й","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"лцлЙЛђЛЂл░лХ 7","runtime":137,"tagline":"┬ФлюлхЛЂЛѓЛї лйлх лилйл░лхЛѓ л│Лђл░лйлИЛє┬╗","homepage":"","overview":"лълйлИ л┐лЙл║лЙЛђлИл╗лИ лблЙл║лИлЙ лИ лалИлЙ, лЏлЙЛЂ-лљлйл┤лХлхл╗лхЛЂ лИ лЏлЙлйл┤лЙлй. лЮлЙ л╝лИЛђ л▒лЙл╗ЛїЛѕлх лйлх лИл│Лђл░лхЛѓ л┐лЙ лИЛЁ л┐Лђл░л▓лИл╗л░л╝. лЌлйлЙл╣ л░Лђл░л▒ЛЂл║лИЛЁ л┐ЛЃЛЂЛѓЛІлйЛї, лйлхл┐ЛђлИл╗лИЛЄлйлЙ л▓ЛІЛЂлЙл║лИлх лйлхл▒лЙЛЂл║Лђлхл▒ЛІ, л╝лИл╗л╗лИлЙлйЛІ л┤лЙл╗л╗л░ЛђлЙл▓ лйл░ л║лЙл╗лхЛЂл░ЛЁ лИ лЙЛЄлхлйЛї, лЙЛЄлхлйЛї лилйл░л╝лхлйлИЛѓЛІл╣ лил╗лЙл┤лхл╣. лАл║лЙЛђлЙЛЂЛѓЛї лйлх лилйл░лхЛѓ л│Лђл░лйлИЛє."},"name":"PЛЃЛЂЛЂл║лИл╣","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"H─▒zl─▒ ve ├ќfkeli 7","runtime":0,"tagline":"Son bir s├╝r├╝┼Ъ.","homepage":"","overview":"H─▒zl─▒ ve ├ќfkeli ekibi, intikam almak isteyen bir ─░ngiliz gizli operasyonlar suikast├Д─▒s─▒ndan gelen tehlikeden habersizdirler. K├╝├Д├╝k karde┼Ъi OwenРђЎ─▒ yaralayanlar─▒ sistematik olarak avlamakta olan Shaw, ekibe verilen Toretto evini havaya u├Дurur. Bunun ├╝zerine Dom, yard─▒m i├Дin ├╝st d├╝zey bir devlet ajan─▒na ba┼Ъvurur. Kahramanlar─▒m─▒z bir kez daha direksiyona ge├Дer. ABD h├╝k├╝meti i├Дin yap─▒lm─▒┼Ъ bir takip cihaz─▒n─▒n ele ge├Дirilmesi gereklidir."},"name":"T├╝rk├Дe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Fast & Furious 7","runtime":138,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Dominic Torettos crew er tilbage i USA efter opg├Иret med Owen Shaw. Men Shaw har en storebror, Deckard, som ├Иnsker h├дvn. Han starter i Tokyo med at dr├дbe en af Doms kammesjukker, og s├Ц f├Цr banden ellers travlt med at tage kampen op. Undervejs f├Цr de en uventet h├Цndsr├дkning af en g├Цdefuld kontakt, der tilbyder Deckard p├Ц et fad, hvis Dom vil hj├дlpe med at befri en kidnappet superhacker i Kaukasus."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":140,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nu Owen Shaw is uitgeschakeld door Dominic Toretto en zijn crew, is Shaw's broer Deckard Shaw uit op wraak. Na de dood van Han, is ook Dominic uit op wraak. Samen met zijn crew en \"Mr. Nobody\" gaan ze op zoek naar een hackprogramma genaamd 'God's Eye', om zo achter Deckard's locatie te kunnen komen en hem uit te schakelen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Velocidade Furiosa 7","runtime":138,"tagline":"A vingan├Дa est├А a chegar.","homepage":"","overview":"Ap├│s derrotarem Owen Shaw, Dominic Toretto (Vin Diesel) e os seus comparsas decidem regressar aos EUA, onde lhes foi concedido o perd├Бo pelas suas infrac├Д├хes e a oportunidade de um recome├Дo, sem qualquer cadastro. ├Ѕ ent├Бo que Dom percebe que o grupo est├А na mira de Deckard, o irm├Бo mais velho de Owen, que jura destruir todos os respons├Аveis pela sua morte."},"name":"Portugu├фs","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"R├йchlo a zbesilo 7","runtime":137,"tagline":"Pomsta dorazila domov.","homepage":"","overview":"V predch├Аdzaj├║com pr├Гbehu zloduch Owen Shaw ob┼Цa┼Йoval na┼Аich hrdinov tak intenz├Гvne, ┼Йe ho museli zastavi┼Ц. Aj ke─Ј ho pritom takmer pripravili o ┼Йivot a v k├│me poslali do nemocnice. Jeho rozhnevan├й star┼А├Г brat Deckart Shaw sa v┼Аak rozhodne, ┼Йe to tak nenech├А a na opl├Аtku priprav├Г o ┼Йivot nielen ich, ale aj ich rodiny a v┼Аetk├йch bl├Гzkych. Bez oh─Йadu na to, ako r├йchli ─Їi zbesil├Г bud├║. A Dominicovi Torettovi, jeho rodine a kamar├Аtom p├┤jde naozaj o ┼Йivot, preto┼Йe Deckart je dokonal├й stroj na zab├Гjanie, ktor├й vycvi─Їila ┼Аpeci├Аlna elitn├А vojensk├А jednotka."},"name":"Sloven─Їina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"Fast & Furious 7","runtime":139,"tagline":"Llega el momento de la venganza.","homepage":"","overview":"Ha pasado un a├▒o desde que el equipo de Dominic Torreto y Brian pudiera regresar finalmente a Estados Unidos, tras ser indultados. Desean adaptarse a una vida en la legalidad, pero el entorno ya no es el mismo. Dom intenta acercarse a Letty, y Brian lucha para acostumbrarse a la vida en una urbanizaci├│n con Mia y su hijo. Ninguno de ellos imagina que un fr├Гo asesino brit├Аnico, entrenado para realizar operaciones secretas, se cruzar├А en sus vidas para convertirse en su mayor enemigo."},"name":"Espa├▒ol","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Hal├Аlos iramban 7","runtime":140,"tagline":"A r├Еgi csapat, m├Еg egy utols├│ k├Хr...","homepage":"http://www.fastandfurious7film.com/","overview":"Miut├Аn v├Еgeztek Owen Shaw-val ├Еs band├Аj├Аval, Dominic, Brian ├Еs a csapat visszat├Еrhetnek az Egyes├╝lt ├Ђllamokba, hogy ism├Еt norm├Аlis ├Еletet ├Еljenek, ahogyan azt tervezt├Еk. De Owen b├Аtyja, Ian Shaw, aki Han hal├Аla ut├Аn l├Еp sz├Гnre, Dominic nyom├Аban van, ├Еs bossz├║t esk├╝szik ├Хccse hal├Аla miatt. A csapat k├Еszen ├Аll, hogy meg├Хlje azt az embert, aki a legjobb bar├Аtjuk hal├Аl