fr├Гo asesino brit├Аnico, entrenado para realizar operaciones secretas, se cruzar├А en sus vidas para convertirse en su mayor enemigo."},"name":"Espa├▒ol","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"п«п┤┘є █и","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"\"п»┌ЕпДп▒п» п┤пД┘ѕ\" (пг█їп│┘ѕ┘є пДп│пфпф┘ЄпД┘Ё) ┘Йп│ пДп▓ ┘Ёп▒┌» пеп▒пДп»п▒п┤пї пе┘Є п»┘єпепД┘ё ┌»п▒┘Ђпф┘є пД┘єпф┘ѓпД┘Ё пДп▓ п»пД┘Ё┘є█ї┌Е пф┘ѕп▒пф┘ѕ (┘ѕ█ї┘є п»█їп▓┘ё) ┘ѕ ┌»п▒┘ѕ┘Єп┤ ┘Ё█їРђїпепДп┤п»..."},"name":"┘ЂпДп▒п│█ї","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"─ђtrs un bez ┼Й─Њlast─Фbas 7","runtime":137,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Vi┼єi ir iekaroju┼Аi Tokiju, Riode┼Йaneiro, Losand┼Йelosu un Londonu, bet pasaul─Њ vairs nesp─Њl─Њ p─Њc vi┼єu noteikumiem. Ar─Ђbijas tuksne┼Аa svelme, nepiekl─Ђj─Фgi augsti debesskr─Ђpji, miljoniem dol─Ђru uz rite┼єiem un ─╝oti, ─╝oti slavens ─╝aundaris. ─ђtrumam nav robe┼Йu."},"name":"Latvie┼Аu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"Forsaj 7","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ozbek","iso_639_1":"uz","iso_3166_1":"UZ","english_name":"Uzbek"},{"data":{"title":"уІѓжЄјТЎѓжђЪ 7","runtime":0,"tagline":"УИЕуЏАт╝ЋТЊј УИЈСИіухѓТЦхСИђуеІ!","homepage":"","overview":"уиіТјЦСИіжЏєТІюС╗Ђ (С┐ЮуЙЁуЇ▓тіа жБЙ) тњїжў┐уЋХ (жЏ▓У┐фу┤а жБЙ) тєЇТгАжЏєтљѕСИђуюЙСИќуЋїу┤џжБіУ╗ітЦйТЅІ№╝їтЇћтіЕУГдТќ╣уиЮТІ┐СИђжџіТЕФУАїТГљТ┤▓уџётЃ▒тѓГтЁхтюў№╝їСИдТ«║ТГ╗тЁХждќжаўтЦДжЏ▓жѓх (уЏДтЁІС╝іжЏ▓Тќ» жБЙ)№╝їС╗ЦТЈЏтЈќТИЁжЎцС╗ќтђЉТГит╣┤СЙєуџёуі»уйфу┤ђжїё№╝їУ┐ћтЏъуЙјтюІУѕЄт«ХС║║жЄЇжЂјТќ░ућЪТ┤╗сђѓтЈ»ТЃютЦйТЎ»СИЇтИИ№╝їтЦДжЏ▓уџётЊЦтЊЦуІётЇАжѓх (уЕЇжЂютЈ▓жЂћжаЊ жБЙ) уфЂуёХтЄ║уЈЙуѓ║т╝Ът╝Ъта▒С╗Є№╝їС╗ќТЏЙтЈЃУѕЄуЅ╣уе«жЃежџіуџёУАїтѕ║С╗╗тІЎ№╝їу╣╝ујЄтЁѕтюеТЮ▒С║гТ«║ТГ╗С║єжЪЊ (тДюТѕљ жБЙ) №╝їтєЇуѓИТ»ђжў┐уЋХуџёт«Хтюњ№╝їТГБт╝ЈтљЉуюЙС║║т«БТѕ░№╝ЂТІюС╗ЂС╗ЦтЈітЁХС╗ќтљїС╝┤С║джЃйТЇ▓тЁЦС║ІС╗Х№╝їУдќтљїС╝┤уѓ║сђїт«ХС║║сђЇуџёжў┐уЋХУфЊУдЂС╗ЦуЅЎжѓёуЅЎУѕЄуІётЇАжѓхТ▒║СИђТГ╗Тѕ░№╝їУѕЄСИђуюЙтЁёт╝ЪУИЈСИіТюђуўІуІѓсђЂТюђуІѓжЄјуџёСИђуеІсђѓ"},"name":"ТЎ«жђџУ»Ю","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Kiired ja vihased 7","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Domi (Vin Diesel) ja Briani (Paul Walker) komando on USAsse tagasi p├Х├Хrdunud ning ├╝ritab kohaneda seaduskuuleka ja rahuliku elustiiliga, mis m├хjub kohati lausa koomiliselt. Seda rahu on otsustanud rikkuda aga eelmises peat├╝kis m├цttasse l├Х├Хdud pahalase Owen ShawРђЎ (Luke Evans) vend Deckard, keda kehastab ├╝liveenvalt sarja uustulnuk Jason Statham. See k├╝lmavereline eks-eri├╝ksuslasest monstrum on asunud oma venna eest k├цtte maksma, alustades Hani (Sung Kang) k├хrvaldamisest Tokyos ning ├╝ritades sama ka Hobbsiga (Dwayne Johnson). Et Deckard ShawРђЎd tabada, p├Х├Хrdub Dom k├хrgetasemelise valitsusagendi (Kurt Russell) poole ning teeb m├хlemale kasuliku diili. Algab globaalne jaht ning seekord pannakse rehvid suitsema nii Abu Dhabis, Los Angeleses, Tokyos kui ka Aserbaid┼Йaanis."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"Hitri in drzni 7","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Hitri dirkalniki, neustra┼Аni vozniki in mi─Їna dekleta se vra─Їajo na velika platna v nadaljevanju zgodbe o drznem vozniku Dominicu in njegovih dirka┼Аkih prijateljih. Po smrti kriminalca Owena se Dominic s svojo ekipo lahko vrne v ZDA in za┼Йivi obi─Їajno ┼Йivljenje, toda na─Їrte jim prekri┼Йa Owenov ma┼А─Їevalni brat Ian. Ta najprej v Tokiu odstrani Dominicovega prijatelja Hana, pod ru┼Аo pa ┼Йeli spraviti tudi druge ─Їlane hitre dru┼А─Їine. Dominic mora zato prijatelje prepri─Їati, da se mu ┼Аe enkrat pridru┼Йijo v norih avtomobilskih dirkah in vrtoglavih dirka┼Аkih podvigih, da bi prekri┼Йali Ianove na─Їrte."},"name":"Sloven┼А─Їina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"п║пДпХпе 7","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"пДп│пф┘Ѓ┘ЁпД┘ё┘ІпД ┘ёпБпГп»пДпФ пД┘ёпБпгп▓пДпА пД┘ёп│пДпе┘ѓпЕпї пеп╣п» ┘Ё┘ѓпф┘ё (пБ┘ѕ┘і┘є п┤┘ѕ) ┘ѕ┘Ђп▒┘і┘ѓ┘Є пБпхпепГ пепЦп│пфпипДп╣пЕ п»┘ѕ┘Ё┘і┘є┘і┘Ѓ (┘ЂпД┘є п»┘іп▓┘і┘ё) ┘ѕпеп▒пД┘іпД┘є (пе┘ѕ┘ё ┘ѕ┘ѕ┘Ѓп▒) ┘ѕ┘Ђп▒┘і┘ѓ┘Є┘ЁпД пД┘ёп╣┘ѕп»пЕ пЦ┘ё┘і пД┘ё┘ѕ┘ёпД┘іпДпф пД┘ё┘ЁпфпГп»пЕ ┘ѕп╣┘іп┤ пГ┘іпДпЕ┘Ї пипе┘іп╣┘іпЕ┘Ї ┘Ё┘Јпгп»п»┘ІпДпї ┘ѕ┘ё┘Ѓ┘є (пЦ┘іпД┘є) пД┘ёпБп« пД┘ёпБ┘Ѓпеп▒ ┘ё┘ђ(пБ┘ѕ┘і┘є) ┘іп│п╣┘і ┘ё┘ёпЦ┘єпф┘ѓпД┘Ё ┘ё┘Ё┘ѓпф┘ё пБп«┘і┘Є ┘Ё┘є п»┘ѕ┘Ё┘і┘є┘і┘Ѓпї ┘ѕпепД┘ёпфпД┘ё┘і пфпх┘Ё┘Ё пД┘ёп╣пхпДпепЕ пепБ┘Ѓ┘Ё┘ё┘ЄпД п╣┘ё┘і пД┘ёпД┘єпф┘ѓпД┘Ё ┘Ё┘є пД┘ёп▒пг┘ё пД┘ёп░┘і ┘ѓпД┘Ё пе┘ѓпф┘ё пхп»┘і┘ѓ┘Є┘Ё."},"name":"пД┘ёп╣п▒пе┘іпЕ","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Arriba el moment de la venjan├Дa.","homepage":"","overview":"De nou els problemes els persegueixen. Sense aconseguir alliberar-se de la taca de criminals de la fitxa. El seu passat de llarga traject├▓ria a les carreres il┬иlegals els perseguir├а i hauran de fer front a les circumst├аncies de l'├║nica manera que saben. Quan els posin entre l'espasa i la paret idearan un pla per escapar del perill en una carrera trepidant per salvar la vida i netejar la seva reputaci├│. Acci├│, persecucions i un ritme fren├еtic en aquesta nova entrega."},"name":"Catal├а","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"рЃцрЃЮрЃарЃАрЃљрЃЪрЃў 7","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"рЃЦрЃљрЃарЃЌрЃБрЃџрЃў","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Яц░ЯцФЯЦЇЯццЯцЙЯц░ ЯцЋЯцЙ ЯцюЯЦЂЯцеЯЦѓЯце 7","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Яц╣Яц┐ЯцеЯЦЇЯцдЯЦђ","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"AT","english_name":"German"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"553ba24592514138a90067c6","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/553ba24592514138a90067c6","author":"Kenechukwu","content":"Revenge is so so cold...... action packed, thrilling and suspense filled but still some bits of make believe tricks here and there. \r\nHow did Hobbs know that there's a need for the drone to be brought down right after leaving the hospital bed? how did he know where the drone was at the moment when he left with the ambulance? How did Deckard Shaw know both that Toretto and his crew will be both on the route of Afghanistan and also when they were at Abu Dhabi? \r\nIts a little bit odd and out of place for the director and script editor.... \r\nAs for the next upcoming part in the franchise, i think Mark Wahlberg should be considered for a part in the rest of Fast and furious franchise..... Cheers ! ! !","created_at":"2015-04-25T14:18:45.571Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:57:34.280Z","author_details":{"name":"Kenechukwu","rating":null,"username":"keneonyinye","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"55d987a692514143f30041fb","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/55d987a692514143f30041fb","author":"Per Gunnar Jonsson","content":"$11","created_at":"2015-08-23T08:43:18.814Z","updated_at":"2024-05-16T15:21:15.023Z","author_details":{"name":"Per Gunnar Jonsson","rating":9,"username":"Dark Jedi","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":337339,"adult":false,"title":"The Fate of the Furious","video":false,"overview":"When a mysterious woman seduces Dom into the world of crime and a betrayal of those closest to him, the crew face trials that will test them as never before.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.2928,"vote_count":10704,"poster_path":"/dImWM7GJqryWJO9LHa3XQ8DD5NH.jpg","release_date":"2017-04-12","vote_average":6.856,"backdrop_path":"/3IJ8kG8i84PncXkSovu0PaZQfjM.jpg","original_title":"The Fate of the Furious","original_language":"en"},{"id":82992,"adult":false,"title":"Fast & Furious 6","video":false,"overview":"Hobbs has Dominic and Brian reassemble their crew to take down a team of mercenaries; Dominic unexpectedly gets sidetracked with facing his presumed deceased girlfriend, Letty.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0789,"vote_count":11045,"poster_path":"/thSmnRdrzPBBospIOJjLZBReqzo.jpg","release_date":"2013-05-21","vote_average":6.814,"backdrop_path":"/oqxCzAO8sn1rSco2Pc19DlitgEn.jpg","original_title":"Fast & Furious 6","original_language":"en"},{"id":51497,"adult":false,"title":"Fast Five","video":false,"overview":"Former cop Brian O'Conner partners with ex-con Dom Toretto on the opposite side of the law. Since Brian and Mia Toretto broke Dom out of custody, they've blown across many borders to elude authorities. Now backed into a corner in Rio de Janeiro, they must pull one last job in order to gain their freedom.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2891,"vote_count":8719,"poster_path":"/gEfQjjQwY7fh5bI4GlG0RrBu7Pz.jpg","release_date":"2011-04-20","vote_average":7.24,"backdrop_path":"/tQN9JEQ4N4aqej7O6AkQtt0dLpt.jpg","original_title":"Fast Five","original_language":"en"},{"id":13804,"adult":false,"title":"Fast & Furious","video":false,"overview":"When a crime brings them back to L.A., fugitive ex-con Dom Toretto reignites his feud with agent Brian O'Conner. But as they are forced to confront a shared enemy, Dom and Brian must give in to an uncertain new trust if they hope to outmaneuver him. And the two men will find the best way to get revenge: push the limits of what's possible behind the wheel.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.036,"vote_count":7692,"poster_path":"/lUtVoRukW7WNtUySwd8hWlByBds.jpg","release_date":"2009-04-02","vote_average":6.688,"backdrop_path":"/25HepicRtrzZ3MVCqhfoxGDbHjw.jpg","original_title":"Fast & Furious","original_language":"en"},{"id":262500,"adult":false,"title":"Insurgent","video":false,"overview":"Beatrice Prior must confront her inner demons and continue her fight against a powerful alliance which threatens to tear her society apart.","genre_ids":[28,878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.1544,"vote_count":10334,"poster_path":"/dP5Fb6YRfzmCQtRbHOr2kO7tJW9.jpg","release_date":"2015-03-18","vote_average":6.363,"backdrop_path":"/8YNNyQiPZlF9qv5EGOUK20mnXVk.jpg","original_title":"Insurgent","original_language":"en"},{"id":99861,"adult":false,"title":"Avengers: Age of Ultron","video":false,"overview":"When Tony Stark tries to jumpstart a dormant peacekeeping program, things go awry and EarthРђЎs Mightiest Heroes are put to the ultimate test as the fate of the planet hangs in the balance. As the villainous Ultron emerges, it is up to The Avengers to stop him from enacting his terrible plans, and soon uneasy alliances and unexpected action pave the way for an epic and unique global adventure.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.5834,"vote_count":24141,"poster_path":"/4ssDuvEDkSArWEdyBl2X5EHvYKU.jpg","release_date":"2015-04-22","vote_average":7.271,"backdrop_path":"/kIBK5SKwgqIIuRKhhWrJn3XkbPq.jpg","original_title":"Avengers: Age of Ultron","original_language":"en"},{"id":9799,"adult":false,"title":"The Fast and the Furious","video":false,"overview":"Dominic Toretto is a Los Angeles street racer suspected of masterminding a series of big-rig hijackings. When undercover cop Brian O'Conner infiltrates Toretto's iconoclastic crew, he falls for Toretto's sister and must choose a side: the gang or the LAPD.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0826,"vote_count":10655,"poster_path":"/gqY0ITBgT7A82poL9jv851qdnIb.jpg","release_date":"2001-06-22","vote_average":7.002,"backdrop_path":"/jY9ef5nqY4xIIMu3yzW3qamUCoi.jpg","original_title":"The Fast and the Furious","original_language":"en"},{"id":241554,"adult":false,"title":"Run All Night","video":false,"overview":"Brooklyn mobster and prolific hit man Jimmy Conlon has seen better days. Longtime best friend of a mob boss, Jimmy is haunted by the sins of his pastРђћas well as a dogged police detective whoРђЎs been one step behind Jimmy for 30 years. But when JimmyРђЎs estranged son becomes a target, Jimmy must make a choice between the crime family he chose and the real family he abandoned long ago. Now, with nowhere safe to turn, Jimmy has just one night to figure out exactly where his loyalties lie and to see if he can finally make things right.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.876,"vote_count":2922,"poster_path":"/iGvSMoPbWZWDnIhh54yiq3sW7wH.jpg","release_date":"2015-03-11","vote_average":6.428,"backdrop_path":"/nzVlhhk9HrIYMFMOGpFNLMtd30u.jpg","original_title":"Run All Night","original_language":"en"},{"id":207703,"adult":false,"title":"Kingsman: The Secret Service","video":false,"overview":"The story of a super-secret spy organization that recruits an unrefined but promising street kid into the agency's ultra-competitive training program just as a global threat emerges from a twisted tech genius.","genre_ids":[80,35,28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.5211,"vote_count":17599,"poster_path":"/r6q9wZK5a2K51KFj4LWVID6Ja1r.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-24","vote_average":7.62,"backdrop_path":"/qzUIOTk0E3F1zjvYjcBRTKUTgf9.jpg","original_title":"Kingsman: The Secret Service","original_language":"en"},{"id":76757,"adult":false,"title":"Jupiter Ascending","video":false,"overview":"In a universe where human genetic material is the most precious commodity, an impoverished young Earth woman becomes the key to strategic maneuvers and internal strife within a powerful dynastyРђд","genre_ids":[878,14,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.6786,"vote_count":7010,"poster_path":"/2NCcAZ3M3F0FxENYmammBknwpVn.jpg","release_date":"2015-02-04","vote_average":5.456,"backdrop_path":"/w4hk4QG05nDuSgimpa7XAM6OyPX.jpg","original_title":"Jupiter Ascending","original_language":"en"},{"id":198184,"adult":false,"title":"Chappie","video":false,"overview":"Every child comes into the world full of promise, and none more so than Chappie: he is gifted, special, a prodigy. Like any child, Chappie will come under the influence of his surroundingsРђћsome good, some badРђћand he will rely on his heart and soul to find his way in the world and become his own man. But there's one thing that makes Chappie different from any one else: he is a robot.","genre_ids":[80,28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.6158,"vote_count":8340,"poster_path":"/uuDUpzlMFomdSfNWlpEPS9nVZWV.jpg","release_date":"2015-03-04","vote_average":6.786,"backdrop_path":"/3pKIcv6KhUE35jsKnv3MylQ3OT2.jpg","original_title":"Chappie","original_language":"en"},{"id":9615,"adult":false,"title":"The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift","video":false,"overview":"In order to avoid a jail sentence, Sean Boswell heads to Tokyo to live with his military father. In a low-rent section of the city, Sean gets caught up in the underground world of drift racing","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.7037,"vote_count":7460,"poster_path":"/46xqGOwHbh2TH2avWSw3SMXph4E.jpg","release_date":"2006-06-03","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/dMARcKLrv0T7kVJ4iQR3vqTTdtT.jpg","original_title":"The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift","original_language":"en"},{"id":260346,"adult":false,"title":"Taken 3","video":false,"overview":"Ex-government operative Bryan Mills finds his life is shattered when he's falsely accused of a murder that hits close to home. As he's pursued by a savvy police inspector, Mills employs his particular set of skills to track the real killer and exact his unique brand of justice.","genre_ids":[53,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.2206,"vote_count":6055,"poster_path":"/vzvMXMypMq7ieDofKThsxjHj9hn.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-16","vote_average":6.26,"backdrop_path":"/vFm4pF0BgaWPj0i2zEiZO6TqEQ0.jpg","original_title":"Taken 3","original_language":"en"},{"id":257091,"adult":false,"title":"Get Hard","video":false,"overview":"When millionaire hedge fund manager James is convicted of fraud and sentenced to a stretch in San Quentin, the judge gives him one month to get his affairs in order. Knowing that he won't survive more than a few minutes in prison on his own, James desperately turns to Darnell-- a black businessman who's never even had a parking ticket -- for help. As Darnell puts James through the wringer, both learn that they were wrong about many things, including each other.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.6033,"vote_count":2855,"poster_path":"/rJPbS2cYOYhDCjT5NmW1Fm6gFl3.jpg","release_date":"2015-03-26","vote_average":6.024,"backdrop_path":"/b52Vpc5NZTdoj1mlcgc9xd14i3i.jpg","original_title":"Get Hard","original_language":"en"},{"id":584,"adult":false,"title":"2 Fast 2 Furious","video":false,"overview":"It's a major double-cross when former police officer Brian O'Conner teams up with his ex-con buddy Roman Pearce to transport a shipment of \"dirty\" money for shady Miami-based import-export dealer Carter Verone. But the guys are actually working with undercover agent Monica Fuentes to bring Verone down.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3206,"vote_count":8009,"poster_path":"/6nDZExrDKIXvSAghsFKVFRVJuSf.jpg","release_date":"2003-06-05","vote_average":6.515,"backdrop_path":"/90ooE5SbUEO0OVJHewNO7pgySb6.jpg","original_title":"2 Fast 2 Furious","original_language":"en"},{"id":265208,"adult":false,"title":"Wild Card","video":false,"overview":"When a Las Vegas bodyguard with lethal skills and a gambling problem gets in trouble with the mob, he has one last playРђд and it's all or nothing.","genre_ids":[53,80,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.6521,"vote_count":1895,"poster_path":"/zN80Tlly8oMpKbVJv2TfRIj8dHG.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-14","vote_average":5.693,"backdrop_path":"/9Xna1fmRkTyAfMSonokrwblYXUS.jpg","original_title":"Wild Card","original_language":"en"},{"id":256591,"adult":false,"title":"Focus","video":false,"overview":"Nicky, an accomplished con artist, gets romantically involved with his disciple Jess but later ends their relationship. Years later, she returns as a femme fatale to spoil his plans.","genre_ids":[107